acity":"","overlay-gradient":""}},"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[106,73,46,114,206,205,439,28,262],"class_list":["post-6555","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-call-to-islam-al-dawah","tag-islam","tag-love-al-mahabbah","tag-manners-adab","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-strength-al-quwwah","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-umar-ibn-al-khattab"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1HJ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":6555,"position":0},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11611,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/salman-king-not-a-khalifah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6555,"position":1},"title":"Salman on Khilafah: Unjust leaders are kings, not Caliphs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman al-Farisi reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to him, \u201cAm I a king or a Caliph?\u201d Salman said, \u201cIf you acquire as much as two coins from the lands of the Muslims, more or less, then you place it where it does not belong,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/27\/umar-ibn-al-khattab-inspired\/","url_meta":{"origin":6555,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Umar: If anyone in Ummah is divinely-inspired, it is Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBefore you were nations with divinely inspired people. If such a person were in my nation, it would surely be Umar.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3689 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14774,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/29\/umar-jahiliyyah-islam-ignorance\/","url_meta":{"origin":6555,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Jahiliyyah: Islam is undone if people do not know ignorance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Taymiyyah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the bonds of Islam will undone, one by one, only if there arise people in Islam who never knew the time of ignorance.\u201d Source: Majmu\u0304' al-Fata\u0304wa\u0301 15\/54 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062a\u064a\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37577,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/umar-tarak-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6555,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Salat: No share of Islam for one who leaves prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miswar ibn Makhramah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is no share of Islam for one who abandons the prayer.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 117 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0631 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0645\u064e\u062e\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u0